Package nsk.enhanced.System.Hibernate

Class WorldEntity

java.lang.Object
nsk.enhanced.System.Hibernate.WorldEntity
@Entity public class WorldEntity extends Object
The WorldEntity class represents a world in the server, stored in the `surveillance_worlds` database table. This class is used to manage and persist world data.
